title: location
ev_biomass_seeds_oct_2019_density_exp: Big Oaks National Wildlife Refuge, Madison, IN, USA

title: plot
ev_biomass_seeds_oct_2019_density_exp: experimental plot, which corresponds to planting treatment (1 - 10)

title: sp
ev_biomass_seeds_oct_2019_density_exp: species (Ev = Elymus virginicus, Mv = Microstegium vimineum)

title: ID
ev_biomass_seeds_oct_2019_density_exp: plant ID (A = focal adult, 1 - 3 = focal seedlings)

title: weight
ev_biomass_seeds_oct_2019_density_exp: dry weight of plant in grams (without seeds)

title: seeds_collected
ev_biomass_seeds_oct_2019_density_exp: indicator variable of whether seeds were present in the sample

title: seeds_green
ev_biomass_seeds_oct_2019_density_exp: indicator variable of seed color (0 = all brown, 0.5 = mixed brown and green, 1 = all green)
